Event staff scan registrations and hand out lanyards at the entrance, while career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops. The engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage, and tech companies display demo screens showcasing their latest apps. A robotics startup captures attention by flying a small drone above its booth. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails. Announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair.
